eep Show (TV series)|Peep Show]]'' || Professor Alistair MacLeish || Series 2, Episode 4: \"[[List of Peep Show episodes#Series 2 (2004)|University Challenge]]\"\n|-\n| 2005 || ''[[The Afternoon Play]]'' || Billy Shannon || Series 3, Episode 5: \"The Singing Cactus\"\n|-\n| 2005\u201312 || ''[[The Thick of It]]'' || [[Malcolm Tucker]] ||\n|-\n| 2005 || ''Destination Scotland'' || Narrator || Documentary\n|-\n| 2005\u201311 || ''Artworks Scotland'' || Narrator/Himself || 4 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" | 2006 || ''Submarine Rescue'' || Narrator || Documentary\n|-\n|''[[Pinochet in Suburbia]]'' || Andy McEntee || Television [[docudrama]]\n|-\n|''[[DNA (TV series)|Donovan]]'' || Dr. Angus Baldwin || Series 1, Episode 3\n|-\n|''[[Trawlermen (TV series)|Trawlermen]]'' || Narrator ||\n|-\n|''[[Midsomer Murders]]'' || Laurence Barker || Series 9, Episode 7: \"[[List of Midsomer Murders episodes#ep50|Death in Chorus]]\"\n|-\n|''Aftersun'' || Jim || Television film\n|-\n|''The Martians and Us'' || Narrator ||\n|-\n|''[[Haunted Hogmanay]]'' || Jeff Wylie || Voice\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[Waking the Dead (TV series)|Waking the Dead]]'' || Lucien Calvin || 2 episodes: \"[[List of Waking the Dead episodes#ep55|The Fall]]\"\n|-\n| 2007\u201308 || ''[[Skins (UK TV series)|Skins]]'' || Mark Jenkins || 4 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2007 || ''[[Fallen Angel (UK TV series)|Fallen Angel]]'' || Henry Appleton ||\n|-\n|''Coming Up'' || Joe || Series 5, Episode 6: \"Brussels\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" | 2008 || ''Inside Hamas'' || Narrator || Documentary\n|-\n|''[[Doctor Who]]'' || Lobus Caecilius || Series 4, Episode 2: \"[[The Fires of Pompeii]]\"\n|-\n|''[[Midnight Man (TV serial)|Midnight Man]]'' || Trevor ||\n|-\n|''[[Glendogie Bogey]]'' || Jeff Wylie || Voice\n|-\n|''Cold Blood'' || Narrator || 6 episodes\n|-\n|''The Man Who Cycled the World'' || Narrator || Documentary\n|-\n|''[[The Devil's Whore]]'' || [[Charles I of England|King Charles I]] ||\n|-\n|''The Perfect TV Detective'' || Narr