bc.co.uk/blogs/doctorwho/entries/3ff87d60-7a92-445e-b34e-cd7bc2732d96|title=Make Your Own Doctor Who Game!|date=15 September 2015|website=BBC|accessdate=1 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Lego Dimensions]]''\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/07/06/peter-capaldi-joins-cast-of-lego-dimensions/157544/|title=Peter Capaldi Joins Cast of LEGO Dimensions|first=Jacob|last=Whritenour|date=6 July 2015|website=HardcoreGamer}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/andyrobertson/2015/07/06/superchargers-dark-edition/|title=Don't Miss Out On 'Skylanders Superchargers' Dark Edition|first=Andy|last=Robertson|date=|website=Forbes|accessdate=30 September 2015}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Artist\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2019\n| [[Lewis Capaldi]]\n| \"[[Someone You Loved]]\"\n| David Simon\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bigissue.com/culture/watch-lewis-capaldis-emotional-new-organ-donor-video-starring-peter-capaldi/|title=Watch Lewis Capaldi\u2019s emotional new organ donor video starring Peter Capaldi|author=Sullivan, Ben|website=[[The Big Issue]]|date=8 February 2019|accessdate=9 February 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Award !! Category !! Work !! Result\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"| 1993 ||rowspan=\"2\"| [[BAFTA Scotland Award]] || Best Actor<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/12716570.Nominations_suggest_honours_could_be_shared_in__apos_tartan_Oscars_apos_/|title=Nominations suggest honours could be shared in 'tartan Oscars'|date=2 October 1993|website=[[The Herald (Glasgow)|The Herald]]|accessdate=20 February 2016}}</ref> || ''[[Soft Top Hard Shoulder]]'' || {{Won}}\n|-\n| Best Short Film<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/12679152.Latin_for_a_dark_room/|title=Latin for a dark room|date=22 March 1994|website=[[The Herald (Glasgow)|The Herald]]|accessdate=27 February 2016}}</ref> ||rowspan=\"8\