a.org/award/2006/television/comedy-performance|title=Comedy Performance in 2006|website=[[BAFTA]]|accessdate=20 February 2016}}</ref> || {{Nominated}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 2008 || [[British Academy Television Award for Best Comedy Performance|Best Comedy Performance]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://awards.bafta.org/award/2008/television/comedy-performance|title=Comedy Performance in 2008|website=[[BAFTA]]|accessdate=20 February 2016}}</ref> || {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[RTS Television Award]] || Best Comedy Performance<ref>{{cite web|url=https://rts.org.uk/award/programme-awards-winners-2007|title=Programme Awards Winners 2007|website=Royal Television Society|accessdate=1 August 2015}}</ref> || {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" | 2009 || [[BAFTA Scotland Award]] || Best Acting Performance in Film<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/scotland/awards/ceremony/nominees-winners/british-academy-scotland-awards-winners-in-2009|title=British Academy Scotland Awards: Winners in 2009|date=8 November 2009|website=[[BAFTA]]|accessdate=20 February 2016}}</ref> || rowspan=\"19\" | ''[[In the Loop]]'' || {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[British Independent Film Award]] || [[BIFA Award for Best Performance by an Actor in a British Independent Film|Best Actor]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bifa.film/awards/winners/2009|title=Winners|website=[[British Independent Film Awards]]|accessdate=20 February 2016}}</ref> || {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[New York Film Critics Online Awards|NYFCO Award]] || Best Ensemble Cast<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2009/12/13/avatar-takes-new-york-online-critics-prize|title='Avatar' takes New York online critics' prize|author=Karger, Dave|date=13 December 2009|website=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=20 February 2016}}</ref> || {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[LAFCA Award]] || [[Los Angeles Film Critics Association Award for Best Supporting Actor|Best Supporting Actor]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/la-critics-honor-monique-christoph-waltz-11711/|title=L.A. Critics